CHANGES
=======

1.1.0 (2022-07-15)
------------------
- Update of the authors e-mail address.
- A new and better example taken from the authors personal blog.
- The tarball created with the "dist" target contains all files now.
- Using a custom date format causes less undefined behavior now, because the
  relevant data structure gets initialized by now.

1.0.0 (2022-07-10)
------------------
- Initial release of slog(1).

0.1 (2022-07-09)
----------------
- First experimental release.